  "prompt": "How do I apply for commercial gas connection in Bangalore?",
  "response": "To apply for a commercial gas connection in Bangalore, follow these steps:\n\n1. Choose a gas provider:\n- Mahanagar Gas Limited (MGL)\n- Indraprastha Gas Limited (IGL)\n\n2. Required documents:\n- Company registration certificate\n- GST registration\n- Identity proof of authorized signatory\n- Address proof of business premises\n- NOC from building owner\n- Property tax receipt\n- Trade license\n- Latest electricity bill\n- PAN card\n- Passport-sized photographs\n\n3. Application process:\n- Visit the gas company's office or website\n- Fill out the commercial gas connection application form\n- Submit all required documents\n- Pay the security deposit and connection charges\n- Schedule site inspection\n\n4. Online application options:\n- Visit official gas provider websites\n- Fill online application form\n- Upload scanned documents\n- Pay application fee online\n\n5. Offline application:\n- Visit nearest gas company branch\n- Submit physical documents\n- Pay fees directly at counter\n\n6. Additional steps:\n- Undergo mandatory site verification\n- Sign agreement\n- Receive connection within specified timeframe\n\nRecommended tips:\n- Keep all documents ready\n- Verify document requirements beforehand\n- Maintain clear communication with gas provider\n\nContact respective gas provider for precise, updated information.",
